                            AFM Mission Statement

   To work in partnership with the REE agencies, their customers and
   partners, and the public by meeting their administrative and financial
   management needs and interests through delivery of responsive and
   effective services in:

   Finance Small Purchasing
   Human Resources Facilities Design and Construction
   Grants and Agreements Personal Property
   Major Contracting and Acquisition Real Estate
   Administrative Information Systems and Technology Safety, Health, and
   the Environment


